# Privacy Policy for Nexon
Last updated: June 13, 2026

## 1. Information We Collect
Nexon may collect the following information:
- Discord user IDs and guild (server) IDs
- Data you voluntarily provide through bot commands
- Server configuration settings

## 2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:
- Provide and maintain the bot's functionality
- Improve and optimize the bot
- Respond to your requests and support needs

## 3. Data Storage
All data is stored locally on the bot's hosting server and is not shared with any third parties.

## 4. Your Rights
You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Request deletion of your personal data
- Request correction of your personal data

## 5. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through Discord.
